00:00:12.994 --> 00:00:16.036
Hi! Welcome to your favorite show Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:28.349 --> 00:00:34.688
We are going to learn today how to cook Guntur famous 
Gongura Talimpu Dish

00:00:42.303 --> 00:00:44.803
Ingredients required for Gongura Talimpu

00:00:44.803 --> 00:00:58.405
Sorrel Leaves, Onions, Garlic, Black Gram, Cumin Seeds, Mustard Seeds,
 Raw Bengal Gram, Green Chillies, Salt, Masala Karam &amp; Oil

00:01:15.287 --> 00:01:20.080
First heat some oil in pan

00:01:23.746 --> 00:01:25.432
Its a dish served with rice

00:01:29.972 --> 00:01:33.791
Add some mustard seeds into the pan 

00:01:37.350 --> 00:01:42.934
We can cook pickle as well as curry from sorrel leaves

00:01:49.877 --> 00:02:00.413
Add some black gram seeds and cumin seeds in to the pan &amp; fry them for a while 

00:02:03.503 --> 00:02:09.878
Add one spoon of raw bengal gram into the pan

00:02:11.443 --> 00:02:17.538
Now add some sliced onions into the pan

00:02:27.612 --> 00:02:33.653
Add 15 peeled garlic cloves into the pan 

00:02:37.477 --> 00:02:41.054
Add some sliced green chillies into the pan &amp; let them fry for a while

00:03:03.364 --> 00:03:10.736
Let the onions fry until they are golden brown in colour

00:03:24.704 --> 00:03:33.124
Now add some cleaned and chopped sorrel leaves into the pan 
&amp; mix them well

00:03:45.926 --> 00:03:56.860
Let it cook for a while until the leaves are cooked well 

00:04:27.684 --> 00:04:40.880
Sorrel leaves must be cleaned and dried for one day before cooking
 so that they can easily be cooked

00:04:46.903 --> 00:05:12.584
Add some salt and red chilli powder masala into the pan &amp; mix well

00:05:29.802 --> 00:05:43.202
To make red chiili powder masala, ground some cumin seeds,
 garlic, coriander seeds, salt, and red chilli powder

00:05:55.397 --> 00:06:04.348
Now take the Gongura Talimpu into a serving bowl

